items.title: Source: Blue Jays close to extending Estrada
items.summary: The Blue Jays are close to agreeing with Marco Estrada on a contract extension, a source told MLB.com's Jon Morosi Tuesday night.
items.content: The Blue Jays are close to agreeing with Marco Estrada on a contract extension, a source told MLB.com's Jon Morosi Tuesday night.

items.title: Lowrie's slam caps A's comeback vs. Tigers
items.summary: Jed Lowrie's eighth-inning grand slam led the A's back from a four-run deficit as Oakland outslugged the Tigers for a 9-8 win Tuesday at Comerica Park.
items.content: Jed Lowrie's eighth-inning grand slam led the A's back from a four-run deficit as Oakland outslugged the Tigers for a 9-8 win Tuesday at Comerica Park.

items.title: Gausman hitting his stride down stretch
items.summary: As the Orioles' playoff hopes fade to a flicker, there haven't been many bright spots over the past two weeks. However, the resurgence of right-hander Kevin Gausman is one of them.
